The paper discusses the use of neural networks with external memory to simulate computer behaviors, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the potential for question-answering tasks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL), and the potential for compositional learning, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV).
